import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { UserServiceService } from '../services/user-service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-all-users', templateUrl: './all-users.component.html', styleUrls: ['./all-users.component.css'] }) export class AllUsersComponent implements OnInit { users:any constructor(private userService:UserServiceService){} ngOnInit(): void { this.userService.getAllUsers().subscribe((res)=>{ this.users=res; },(err)=>{ alert("Something went wrong"); }) } }
